#: sites/updates.thunderbird.net/includes/donation-blocked-notice.html:7 sites/www.thunderbird.net/includes/donation-blocked-notice.html:7
msgid "Your browser or an extension might be blocking our donation platform, Fundraise Up."
msgstr "Ваш прегледање или проширење можда блокирају нашу платформу за донације, Fundraise Up."

#: sites/updates.thunderbird.net/includes/donation-blocked-notice.html:10 sites/www.thunderbird.net/includes/donation-blocked-notice.html:10
msgid "Please try again using a different browser, or temporarily disabling the extension."
