#: sites/updates.thunderbird.net/thunderbird/128.0/monthly/index.html:68 sites/updates.thunderbird.net/thunderbird/128.0/monthly/index.html:71
#: sites/updates.thunderbird.net/thunderbird/128.0/monthly/index.html:81 sites/updates.thunderbird.net/thunderbird/128.0/monthly/index.html:84
