msgstr "Thunderbird је поклон од људи попут вас."

#: sites/www.thunderbird.net/desktop/index.html:164 sites/www.thunderbird.net/mobile/index.html:163
msgid "Thousands have contributed time and money to make Thunderbird possible. Its code is open source and freely licensed to use, modify, and share. Thunderbird isn't just free, it makes you free."
