#: sites/www.thunderbird.net/desktop/index.html:195 sites/www.thunderbird.net/mobile/index.html:193
msgid "Level up your Thunderbird Skills."
msgstr "Унапредите своје Thunderbird вештине."

#: sites/www.thunderbird.net/desktop/index.html:200 sites/www.thunderbird.net/mobile/index.html:198
